类 OutputRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.metrics.spi.OutputRecord

  • @InterfaceAudience.Public
@InterfaceStability.Evolving
public class OutputRecord
extends Object
    Represents a record of metric data to be sent to a metrics system.
